OL,3,CFour arrests and several homes
OL,4,Cevacuated after house fire
OL,6,FFour people have been arrested after a
OL,7,Fhouse fire, which led to several homes
OL,8,Fbeing evacuated in the early hours of
OL,9,Fthe morning.
OL,11,FSouth Wales Police said that all four
OL,12,Fhave been arrested on suspicion of
OL,13,Farson with intent to endanger life.
OL,15,FEmergency services were called to the
OL,16,Fblaze on Protheroe Street, Ferndale,
OL,17,Fat around 1:30am on Monday morning
OL,18,F(July 28).
