OL,6,FSeveral neighbouring homes along the
OL,7,Frow of terraced houses were evacuated
OL,8,Fby officers for safety reasons.
OL,10,FA spokesperson for South Wales Police
OL,11,Fsaid: "Fortunately, despite the
OL,12,Fferocity of the fire, there have been
OL,13,Fno reports of any serious injuries
OL,14,Falthough a few residents were treated
OL,15,Ffor smoke inhalation.
