OL,3,CFour arrests and several homes
OL,4,Cevacuated after house fire
OL,6,F"Early indications reveal that the
OL,7,Ffire was started deliberately. Within
OL,8,F30 minutes of the fire being reported,
OL,9,Fa car was proactively stopped by
OL,10,Fofficers from our Roads Policing Unit
OL,11,Fand three men aged 18, 19 and 23 and a
OL,12,F19-year-old woman were arrested on
OL,13,Fsuspicion of arson with intent to
OL,14,Fendanger life. All four remain in
OL,15,Fpolice custody."
