OL,3,CFour arrests and several homes
OL,4,Cevacuated after house fire
OL,6,FA police cordon remains in place on
OL,7,FProtheroe Street as investigations
OL,8,Fcontinue. Emergency services and
OL,9,Fofficials said they are managing the
OL,10,Ffire's impact on those affected and
OL,11,Fthe wider community.
OL,13,FA rest centre has been set up by the
OL,14,Flocal authority to support those
OL,15,Fdisplaced by the incident.
OL,17,FSouth Wales Fire & Rescue Service sent
OL,18,Fmultiple fire engines, a water bowser
OL,19,Fand specialist support units to the
OL,20,Fscene and extinguished the fire by 7am.
