OL,6,FSouth Wales Police added that local
OL,7,Fresidents rallied together to support
OL,8,Fthose families affected. They thanked
OL,9,Fthe community for their understanding
OL,10,Fand co-operation during the ongoing
OL,11,Finvestigation.
OL,13,FA joint investigation by South Wales
OL,14,FPolice and South Wales Fire & Rescue
OL,15,FService has begun and anyone with
OL,16,Fdoorbell or CCTV footage from
OL,17,Fproperties on Protheroe Street, Brown
OL,18,FStreet, Irfon Street, and New Street
OL,19,Ffrom 10pm on Sunday July 27 to 2am
OL,20,Fthis morning, Monday July 28, are
OL,21,Furged to contact emergency services.
